{"tid":1541128,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"車路士香港球迷會指球會官方不贊同批警聲明","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T03:40:23.000Z","uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e240a52abb0bf176c55f8cf6eb46cefaeec38d08","tid":1541128,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:39:18.000Z","msg":"閱讀全文： <a href=\"https://wp.me/p75t7v-7il\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp75t7v-7il&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJM22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=a3e935c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://wp.me/p75t7v-7il</a><br />\n<br />\n車路士香港球迷會發表一則以主席Tommy署名的澄清聲明，聲明以英文寫成，表明早前不接納警察的聲明（於9月1日發出）不代表球會立場。其內容大致有三點：一、球會官方不贊同有關聲明；二、球迷會謝絕警員加入只是出於安全考慮；三、球迷會保持政見中立，亦不代表會員發表任何政治立場。 不過，球迷會專頁並未刪除該份與警察割席的聲明。"},{"pid":"58cb45e964abd870899aa0fd61e9e5e428743a25","tid":1541128,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:40:37.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf3a88dd360d0ec9efd66db4692b2a104121013","tid":1541128,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"After consulting other committee members, I would like to clear up a few things about my previous statement:<br />\n<br />\n1. The statement was not endorsed by Chelsea Football Club.<br />\n<br />\n2. Our intent was not to discriminate against anyone. Our main concern was the safety of our members, which we still believe is of utmost importance going forward.<br />\n<br />\n3. We are an inclusive supporters club and we will continue to welcome members from all walks of life, as long as they have a love for Chelsea Football Club. As a supporters club, we vow to remain politically neutral and will not make any political stance on behalf of our members.<br />\n<br />\nHopefully this clears up 